      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p class="muted">The App works without an account. Health/activity data is stored <strong>locally</strong> on
        your device. Currently <strong>no server transfer</strong> and <strong>no tracking</strong>. Subscription
        status (Free/Lite/Pro) is stored locally as a flag.</p>

      <h2>Categories of Data</h2>
      <ul class="muted">
        <li>App usage data (goals/config, daily values, task progress, XP/level, streaks, achievements)</li>
        <li>Subscription flags (plan, access rights, ads flag – no active ads now)</li>
        <li>Permissions: optional notifications (system consent)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Purposes &amp; Legal Bases</h2>
      <ol class="muted">
        <li>App functionality (Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR)</li>
        <li>Consent (Art. 6(1)(a) GDPR), e.g., notifications</li>
        <li>Legitimate interests (Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR)</li>
      </ol>

      <h2>Storage / Retention</h2>
      <p class="muted">Local on your device until you uninstall or reset the data.</p>

      <h2>Recipients / Third Countries</h2>
      <p class="muted">No external recipients, no international transfers. If we later integrate services, we’ll
        inform you transparently and obtain any required consents.</p>

      <h2>Data Subject Rights</h2>
      <p class="muted">Rights under Arts. 15–21 GDPR. Withdraw consent anytime. You may lodge a complaint with a
        supervisory authority.</p>

      <h2>Minors</h2>
      <p class="muted">Not intended for children under 16.</p>

      <h2>Security</h2>
